{"tid":167252,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"架車油針唔準","createTime":"2017-03-22T16:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T22:23:29.000Z","uid":26108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05e00b4c021de86ed26a592b640557980e37400d","tid":167252,"uid":26108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"小弟揸緊部思域仔（2000年）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁買番黎果陣入$200 （-$2..2 shell) 都係行到200km 左右先到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  圍起都係1蚊1公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最近入$200 行左140 左右都見底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有時停燈位就著油燈但一行車就冇著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下係唔係舊車係咁定要去車房攪攪佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為見到d人話其實油針係唔準但我又冇理由見佢到底都唔入架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"3f1bc890bff5c913069524d0209e43e19c4615e9","tid":167252,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:45:55.000Z","msg":"油針定係油錶唔準呀"},{"pid":"57c36543e39e19bc7ffdaa99caef1c0ea66d2fce","tid":167252,"uid":26108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:50:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>油針定係油錶唔準呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該叫油錶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 之前都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係前排換左前面果2條軚之後先係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但朋友又話唔太關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb790c6e3d320725e58